Cyberwolf, would you mind posting for LadyHawk?

::DevilDuer/Coput/Gawd-bot::

DevilDuer feels the shuttle smash into the shields, almost flying up but Gawd-bot smashes into the back of his chair and nearly squishes him before flying out of the back. DevilDuer gets out of his chair, seeing Coput in stasis lock.

"This is all your fault," he blaims the bot as he grabs him, taking out a pistol and shooting the shuttle's window out, then jumping out of it with Coput, the two bots flying down toward the side of the Iron Fist.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Gawd-bot smashes into the side of the Iron Fist, bouncing off and smashing into the ground. He jumps up. "Oh yeah! Did you see what the immortal just did!"

Gawd-bot glances up at the shuttle, his smile dissapearing. "Uh oh..." he says as the shuttle scrapes the side of the Iron Fist, a loud screeching sound originating from it before the shuttle passes and falls into the ocean.
